name: COVID Icon Set
description:
The Streamline COVID icon set is one the most comprehensive icon sets available and is open-source. A free vector pack with 147 icons to fight the Covid pandemic and keep people safe. Icons have a 1.5px stroke on 24px grid. The strokes are fully editable strokes.
